sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>(Platform Auth)
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Endpoint<br/>HTTPS TLS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant VecDB as Vector DB<br/>(Milvus/PgVector/Qdrant)
    participant KF as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Platform-managed auth
        Proxy->>LS: HTTP/8321<br/>Forwarded request
        LS->>vLLM: POST inference request<br/>HTTPS, Bearer token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>LS: Completion response<br/>HTTPS
        LS->>PG: Store inference log<br/>PostgreSQL/5432, Username/password
        PG-->>LS: ACK
        LS-->>Proxy: JSON response
        Proxy-->>Client: Chat completion result
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,VecDB: Flow 2: RAG Query with Vector I/O
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/vector-io/query<br/>Platform-managed auth
        Proxy->>LS: HTTP/8321<br/>Forwarded request
        LS->>vLLM: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>HTTPS, Bearer token<br/>Generate query embedding
        vLLM-->>LS: Embedding vector
        LS->>VecDB: Vector similarity search<br/>Protocol varies by backend<br/>Token/password auth
        VecDB-->>LS: Relevant documents
        LS->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS, Bearer token<br/>Context-augmented inference
        vLLM-->>LS: Generated response
        LS-->>Proxy: RAG response with citations
        Proxy-->>Client: Augmented response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Evaluation via Kubeflow
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/eval/run<br/>Platform-managed auth
        Proxy->>LS: HTTP/8321<br/>Forwarded request
        LS->>KF: Submit evaluation pipeline<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer token (KUBEFLOW_PIPELINES_TOKEN)
        KF->>S3: Read evaluation dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
        S3-->>KF: Dataset artifacts
        KF->>vLLM: Run model inference<br/>HTTPS, Bearer token
        vLLM-->>KF: Model outputs
        KF-->>LS: Evaluation results<br/>HTTPS
        LS->>PG: Store evaluation results<br/>PostgreSQL/5432
        PG-->>LS: ACK
        LS-->>Proxy: Evaluation summary
        Proxy-->>Client: Evaluation results
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Client,LS: Flow 4: Safety-Shielded Inference
        participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>HTTPS TLS
        Client->>Proxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with safety shield)
        Proxy->>LS: HTTP/8321
        LS->>FMS: POST safety check (input)<br/>HTTPS, custom cert (FMS_SSL_CERT_PATH)
        FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict (pass/block)
        alt Input passes safety check
            LS->>vLLM: POST inference<br/>HTTPS, Bearer token
            vLLM-->>LS: Generated response
            LS->>FMS: POST safety check (output)<br/>HTTPS, custom cert
            FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict
            LS-->>Proxy: Safe response
        else Input blocked
            LS-->>Proxy: Safety violation response
        end
        Proxy-->>Client: Final response
    end
